24x152_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/26-2620324x153_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/26-2620324x154_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>且</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19124-formula679"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/26-2620324x155_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>所以<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/26-2620324x156_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/26-2620324x157_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的一个CPT-框架。</p><p>(2)</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19124-formula680"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/26-2620324x158_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><disp-formula id="hanspub.19124-formula681"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/26-2620324x159_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><disp-formula id="hanspub.19124-formula682"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/26-2620324x160_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><disp-formula id="hanspub.19124-formula683"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/26-2620324x161_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>则</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/26-2620324x162_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/26-2620324x163_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/26-2620324x164_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/26-2620324x165_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula></p><p>且</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19124-formula684"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/26-2620324x166_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>得</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19124-formula685"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/26-2620324x167_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>从而<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/26-2620324x168_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为这个PT-对称量子系统的一组测量算子。</p></sec><sec id="s6"><title>4. 结论</title><p>本文得出了在PT-对称量子系统中的量子测量，即量子测量由一组测量<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/26-2620324x169_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>描述，测量后系统的状态为：<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/26-2620324x170_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。并且通过两组测量算子<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/26-2620324x171_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/26-2620324x172_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>和<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/26-2620324x173_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/26-2620324x174_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/26-2620324x175_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/26-2620324x176_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>得到了PT-对称量子系统中关于量子测量的两个结果。</p></sec><sec id="s7"><title>基金项目</title><p>国家自然科学基金(批准号：11571213)。</p></sec><sec id="s8"><title>文章引用</title><p>杨丽丽,陈峥立,孙海鹏. PT-对称量子理论中的量子测量Quantum Measurement of PT-Symmetric Quantum Theory[J]. 应用数学进展, 2016, 05(04): 790